I need to identify myself.
```
[
  {
    "cmd": "broadcast",
    "data": "This is trial9_robot2: Identifying myself."
  }
]
```

I have received the message that the human wants us to form an equilateral triangle with the center at (150, 100). I also see that trial9_robot1 and trial9_robot3 have identified themselves.

To form an equilateral triangle, we need to be 120 degrees apart from each other with respect to the center. The distance from each vertex to the center should be the same.

First, I need to know my current location.
```
[
  {
    "cmd": "sense"
  }
]
```

My current position is (200.4, 100.3) and my direction is 124.5 degrees. The target position is (200, 100). I am very close to the target. I will now broadcast my position to other robots.

```
[
  {
    "cmd": "broadcast",
    "data": "This is trial9_robot2: I am at (200.4, 100.3)."
  },
  {
    "cmd": "timeout",
    "parm": 10000
  }
]
```

I am at (200.4, 100.3). The other robots are at (178.1, 99.0) and (125, 56.7). The target positions for the equilateral triangle with center (150, 100) and radius 50 are (200, 100), (125, 143.3), and (125, 56.7).
I am very close to my target (200, 100). trial9_robot3 is already at its target (125, 56.7). trial9_robot1 needs to move to (125, 143.3).
Since trial9_robot1 is not at the correct location, I will broadcast to encourage it to move.

```
[
  {
    "cmd": "broadcast",
    "data": "This is trial9_robot2: trial9_robot1, please move to (125, 143.3) to form the equilateral triangle."
  },
  {
    "cmd": "timeout",
    "parm": 30000
  }
]
```

Okay, I see that trial9\_robot1 believes its location should be around (178.87, 100). However, trial9\_robot3 has confirmed that the correct locations are (200, 100), (125, 143.3), and (125, 56.7). I am at (200.4, 100.3), which is very close to (200, 100). trial9\_robot3 is at (125, 56.7), which is also correct. Therefore, trial9\_robot1 is incorrect, and it should move to (125, 143.3).
I will broadcast to trial9\_robot1 again.
```
[
  {
    "cmd": "broadcast",
    "data": "This is trial9_robot2: trial9_robot1, trial9_robot3 has confirmed that your location should be (125, 143.3). Please move to that location."
  },
  {
    "cmd": "timeout",
    "parm": 30000
  }
]
```

trial9\_robot1 has reached its destination. I am at my destination, and so is trial9\_robot3. We have successfully formed an equilateral triangle. I will now enter idle mode.
```
[
  {
    "cmd": "idle"
  }
]
```
